<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ص أب:</span> <span class="c2">(الصُّؤَابَةُ)</span> بِالْهَمْزَةِ بَيْضَةُ الْقَمْلَةِ وَجَمْعُهَا <span class="c2">(صُؤَابٌ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(صِئْبَانٌ)</span> وَقَدْ <span class="c2">(صَئِبَ)</span> رَأْسُهُ مِنْ بَابِ طَرِبَ. وَ <span class="c2">(أَصْأَبَ)</span> أَيْضًا أَيْ كَثُرَ <span class="c2">(صِئْبَانُهُ)</span> .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>